        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs. 6–11. Deretaphrus biology. 6) Series of D. viduatus depicting size variability; 7) Pupal cell of Trichaulax philipsii; 8) D. puncticollis, pupal cocoon mass (with emerging adult) attached to larva of T. philipsii; 9) D. puncticollis, with pupal cocoon; 10) D. xanthorrhoeae, pupal cocoon; 11) D. viduatus, pupal cocoon with silken threads and smooth external surface." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4907462/files/figure.png" .

